  <brief_title>Marimastat Following Chemotherapy in Treating Patients With Small Cell Lung Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase III Study of Marimastat in Patients With Small Cell Lung Cancer Following a Response to First Line Chemotherapy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
